<title>
Vérification de l&#39;ensemble de thermostat (intégré au capteur ECT) 
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Vérifier que la soupape de purge d&#39;air (1) de l&#39;ensemble de thermostat est propre. 
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vérifier si le siège de soupape (2) est exempt de corps étrangers qui pourraient en compromettre l&#39;étanchéité de la soupape. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V20A161006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.019mm" ver = "01" gw = "123" gh = "128"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.968in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Granulés de cire 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vérifier l&#39;ensemble de thermostat comme suit. 
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "ordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Immerger l&#39;ensemble de thermostat (1) dans de l&#39;eau et la faire chauffer progressivement. 
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Ne jamais immerger le connecteur de capteur ECT dans l&#39;eau. 
</ptxt>
</attention2>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vérifier si les granulés de cire commencent à s&#39;ouvrir à une température bien définie. 
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Température à laquelle la soupape commence à s&#39;ouvrir (hauteur d&#39;ouverture de 0,05 mm (0,002 in)): 
</title>
<ptxt>
86,5 – 89,5 &#176;C (187,7 – 193,1 &#176;F)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>
Température à laquelle la soupape est complètement ouverte: 
</title>
<ptxt>
100 &#176;C (212 &#176;F)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>
Hauteur d&#39;ouverture de soupape: 
</title>
<ptxt>
Plus de 8 mm (0,3 in) à 100 &#176;C (212 &#176;F)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure page = "2">
<graphic graphicname = "I7V20A161007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.148mm" ver = "01" gw = "103" gh = "123"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.291in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.328in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.265in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Réchauffeur 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Thermomètre 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</item>
</list2>
<item>
<ptxt>
Si le résultat de la vérification n&#39;est pas satisfaisant, remplacer l&#39;ensemble de thermostat. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A1606008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
